<A>__{watts carves into the cliff with the excavator's digger arm. silt and boulders fall into the yawning trench below. she brings a water cannon to bear: uses its jet to blast away loose silt and stones. the cliff face collapses: a muddy landslide into the deeps. watts backs away from the collapse, thrusters whirring to keep her out of the turbulence. a cloud of silt clears. in her floodlight beams, the obelisk stands revealed its outlines worn by the ages. easily thirty feet tall. watts stares at the obelisk, stunned. her voice is husky:}
